Joe,

The VDO CHT sensors can be bought separately as they can be easily broken when
changing spark plugs. On the TIV engine the recommended location is under #3
plug as it is deemed to be the hottest. Do a search and make sure you get the
right diameter sensor for the plug.

Martin.
